- "tongues" and "genres" are metaphorical expressions referring to languages and document types, respectively; 
- "release years" represent the year the document was published; 
- "active" implies is_active = 1.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT doc_id) 
FROM access_logs 
WHERE access_type = 'download';

SELECT doc_title, year_name
FROM documents
INNER JOIN years ON documents.year = years.year_id;
